</content>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <id>tag:developers.flattr.net,2012-01-24:/api/changelog/add_image_to_thing/</id>
    <title type="html">Added image attribute to thing</title>
    <published>2012-01-23T23:00:00Z</published>
    <updated>2012-01-23T23:00:00Z</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://developers.flattr.net/api/changelog/add_image_to_thing/"/>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Now the thing resource includes a &lt;code&gt;image&lt;/code&gt; attribute with the image to
the thing. If the &lt;code&gt;image&lt;/code&gt; attribute is empty there is no image
available.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
